<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239887>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. MZUSP 117108, 67.9 mm SL, holotype of Moenkhausia lineomaculata, Brazil, Mato Grosso State, Campos de Júlio, rio Juruena, upper rio Tapajós basin." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239888>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Not preserved live specimen of Moenkhausia lineomaculata, Brazil, Mato Grosso State, Sapezal, rio Juruena, upper rio Tapajós basin. Part of the lower lobe of the caudal fin is missing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239888/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239890>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Distribution map of Moenkhausia lineomaculata (yellow dots) in the upper rio Juruena basin, Brazil. White star symbol represents the type locality. Each symbol may represent more than one collection event." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

